question:
2. Find all continuous positive functions \( f(x) \), for \( 0 \leq x \leq 1 \), such that
\[
\begin{array}{c}
\int_{0}^{1} f(x) d x=1 \\
\int_{0}^{1} f(x) x d x=\alpha \\
\int_{0}^{1} f(x) x^{2} d x=\alpha^{2}
\end{array}
\]
where \( \alpha \) is a given real number.

